content: Excellent game, but terribly difficult. The levels are long, and if you make a single mistake, you start at the beginning. Trains have to avoid each other, which is usually easy because you can tell them to stop, but they also have to avoid automobiles, which is incredibly difficult because you can NOT tell them to stop.you have to gauge the train's speed with the automobile's speed to determine if the train can cross the road in time. There is no leeway whatsoever in the collision detection.
